      "content": "it’s just... i look at her and i see how much she has to do, and then she has to deal with me too. i feel like i'm just taking up space and making her life harder. sometimes i think it would just be more peaceful for everyone if i wasn't such a weight on them. i don't want to be a problem anymore.",
